additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: For external use only. Not recommended for any other purpose. Avoid contact with eyes. If sensitivity occurs discontinue use. Contains naturally derived ethanol. Not for use in an oil burner. Keep out of reach of children. FIRST AID: For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (Aust, 131 126, NZ 0800 764 766) or a doctor at once. If swallowed, do NOT induce vomiting
